window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Nothing brings change like war.</b></p> <p>A surge of new tech. New weapons. New tactics.</p> <p>To lead a crew to victory, a captain must understand change.</p> <p>He must understand command, and that it is a test.</p> <p>A test most men fail.</p> <p>He must be brilliant.</p> <p>Resourceful.</p> <p>Every second.</p> <p>Of every day.</p> <p>And at night, during scarce moments of rest, he must sleep the sleep of the righteous.</p> <p>The time has come for Commander Tad Thatcher to look in the mirror.</p> <p>The time has come to ask himself:</p> <p><i>Am I that kind of man?</i></p> <p><b><i>Spacers, Part 2</i></b><b> contains </b><b><i>Wartorn Cluster</i></b><b> through to the end of </b><b><i>The Fall</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
